workout_items.info:
We're continuing on with the same hip opening sequence. If you were a bit tight last week, note where you managed to get to and match or slightly increase it this week. 

- 10 Side To Sides each leg
- Standing Pancake
- 10 Side To Sides each leg
- Side Lean each leg ( 1 min )
- Pigeon Hold each leg (2 mins)
